<template>
  123
</template>

<script setup>
import * as echarts from 'echarts'

onMounted(() => {
  // console.log(chartRef.value);
  myChart.value = echarts.init(chartRef.value as HTMLElement)
  let option = {
    series: [
      {
        type: 'gauge',
        axisLine: {
          lineStyle: {
            width: 10,
            color: [
              [0.3, '#67e0e3'],
              [0.7, '#37a2da'],
              [1, '#fd666d']
            ]
          }
        },
        pointer: {
          itemStyle: {
            color: 'inherit'
          }
        },
        axisTick: {
          distance: 0,
          length: 8,
          lineStyle: {
            color: [
              [0.3, '#67e0e3'],
              [0.7, '#37a2da'],
              [1, '#fd666d']
            ],
            width: 2
          }
        },
        splitLine: {
          distance: 0,
          length: 10,
          lineStyle: {
            color: '#2b5182',
            width: 4
          }
        },
        axisLabel: {
          color: 'inherit',
          distance: 10,
          fontSize: 5
        },
        detail: {
          valueAnimation: true,
          formatter: '{value} ',
          fontSize: 14,
          color: 'inherit',
        },
        data: [
          {
            value: 6.34
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  };
  myChart.value.setOption(option)
})




</script>
<style scoped>


</style>
